{"tid":1525994,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警記招：記者可否現場接力示威？","createTime":"2019-09-01T03:52:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T04:36:36.000Z","uid":286825,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7e93bc30eea68839dd5c6bb0fc119f530d4d2f9f","tid":1525994,"uid":286825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:52:46.000Z","msg":"記者係黑警記者會時，<br />\n直接係鏡頭面前「汁」班大sir得唔得？<br />\n其實市民係信記者多d，因為你地係專業人士，<br />\n目的係要睇到既淺黃轉深黃。<br />\n<br />\n我有幾個建議：<br />\n<br />\n1.黑警話唔撚關佢事既時候，係佢面前放影片，做大圖對住攝影機。<br />\n<br />\n2.必要時直接打斷佢講野，唔洗跟規矩，你地受過邏輯訓練，無可能講唔贏佢地<br />\n<br />\n3.佢話適當武力既時間，問d黑警，「你要唔要我同你做個測試？」你企係到比我用警棍打。<br />\n<br />\n4.無野做到既時候就杯葛記者會，唔好撚去。<br />\n<br />\n我知讀傳理既新聞界朋友，會認為咁有違「中立」既採訪原則，但呢d可能只係舊有既思想。外面既勇武都升級左，記者可唔可以升級下你地既採訪？唔係講野大聲就無禮貌架！<br />\n<br />\n公司比得萬幾兩萬你地，隨時搵過份工都有！我係過來人，怕咩撚野。<br />\n<br />\n不平則嗚，為公義發聲，唔係規規矩矩，你問由得佢慢慢鬼辯。"},{"pid":"f3a75ba8b60037dadab7c89cdbeb0aaef2145581","tid":1525994,"uid":169262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:54:19.000Z","msg":"901 機場攻略<br />\n麻煩大家用盡所有方法傳開佢<br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: red;\">準時</span>到機場，唔係一點先出門口<br />\n- 衣着同裝備冇任何限制，最緊要保護自己<br />\n- 集合地點：機場巴士總站(暢達路)<br />\n- 測試方法：排隊戰術，見到<span style=\"color: red;\">有隊就排</span>；利用人數優勢，<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好單獨行事</span><br />\n- 唔好同任何遊客有肢體碰撞<br />\n- 去機場：<span style=\"color: red;\">以巴士為優先</span>，機場快線集中係香港同青衣站上車<br />\n- 已經準備左幾套應變方案，根據現場情況<span style=\"color: red;\">隨時轉變</span>，要密切留意住 901 機場 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8b%2FUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=44d4c2c1\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P5XusdO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP5XusdO.jpg&h=31adcd48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cTXKf68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcTXKf68.jpg&h=74d57433&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qAxaV7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqAxaV7a.jpg&h=13c2eb06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/otZAnNa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FotZAnNa.jpg&h=f10fa124&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fa0d441ba24279511e49b4ba2c4dc10fed5c0c83","tid":1525994,"uid":162541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:02:41.000Z","msg":"攞片攞圖出黎掀穿佢個大話<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n變相報導真相<br />\n唔會有違記者中立"},{"pid":"0ec3912fcefd0a206a6eb76e1b706207b77ebfa5","tid":1525994,"uid":286825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa0d441ba24279511e49b4ba2c4dc10fed5c0c83","tid":1525994,"uid":162541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:02:41.000Z","msg":"攞片攞圖出黎掀穿佢個大話<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n變相報導真相<br />\n唔會有違記者中立"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:04:15.000Z","msg":"真係唔明香港記者幾時變得咁乖"},{"pid":"e54fd5ffd563cff2aa565f8c8630fa9922d89ce3","tid":1525994,"uid":162541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ec3912fcefd0a206a6eb76e1b706207b77ebfa5","tid":1525994,"uid":286825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa0d441ba24279511e49b4ba2c4dc10fed5c0c83","tid":1525994,"uid":162541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:02:41.000Z","msg":"攞片攞圖出黎掀穿佢個大話<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n變相報導真相<br />\n唔會有違記者中立"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:04:15.000Z","msg":"真係唔明香港記者幾時變得咁乖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:36:36.000Z","msg":"Chur住班警啦，次次講大話，迫佢地講真話"}]}